  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d82\u0dc4: \u0daf\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dc3 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil Wickremesinghe: Swearing in as President amid tight security",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe was sworn in as the eighth Executive President of Sri Lanka today (July 21) amid heavy security.",
        "He became the Prime Minister of Sri Lanka on six occasions and came to the 09th Parliament on 23 June 2021 for the only member of parliament that was won by the United National Party from the national list in the 2020 general election.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe, as a member of a party that has only one member of Parliament, has been given the prime ministership and the president of the country has been receiving a lot of attention worldwide."
      ],
